headline: Union Pacific, Norfolk Southern roll out new domestic intermodal
summary: Following similar interline moves by competing railroads, merger partners Union Pacific and Norfolk Southern have introduced an array of new domestic intermodal services. The post Union Pacific, Norfolk Southern roll out new domestic intermodal appeared first on FreightWaves.
